%pyspark

moon_num = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/moon/num.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
moon_pos = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/moon/pos.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
moon_word = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/moon/word.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
unifi_num = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/unification/num.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
unifi_pos = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/unification/pos.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
unifi_word = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/unification/word.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
dprk_num = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/dprk/num.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
dprk_pos = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/dprk/pos.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")
dprk_word = spark.read.load("hdfs:///user/maria_dev/project/result/dprk/word.csv/", format="csv", sep=",", inferSchema="true", header="true", encoding="utf-8")


moon_num.registerTempTable("mnum")
moon_pos.registerTempTable("mpos")
moon_word.registerTempTable("mword")
unifi_num.registerTempTable("unum")
unifi_pos.registerTempTable("upos")
unifi_word.registerTempTable("uword")
dprk_num.registerTempTable("dnum")
dprk_pos.registerTempTable("dpos")
dprk_word.registerTempTable("dword")

%angular

%angular

%angular

전체 언급량

%sql

select CAST(n.date AS DATE), n.count as president_moon, u.count as reunification, d.count as north_korea
from mnum n 
inner join unum u
on n.date = u.date
inner join dnum d
on n.date = d.date
order by date

%sql

%angular

전체 긍 · 부정 추이

%sql

select CAST(n.date AS DATE), n.sentiment, n.percent as president_moon, u.percent as reunification, d.percent as north_korea
from mpos n 
inner join upos u
on n.date = u.date and n.sentiment = u.sentiment
inner join dpos d
on n.date = d.date and n.sentiment = d.sentiment 
order by date

%angular

문재인 긍 · 부정 추이

%sql

select CAST(n.date AS DATE), n.sentiment, n.percent as president_moon
from mpos n 
order by date

%angular

북한 긍 · 부정 추이

%sql

select CAST(date AS DATE), sentiment, u.percent as unification
from upos u
order by date

%angular

통일 긍 · 부정 추이

%sql

select CAST(date AS DATE), sentiment, percent as dprk
from dpos
order by date
